1
00:01:27,440 --> 00:01:31,880
[The Dark Romance]

2
00:01:32,170 --> 00:01:34,920
[Episode 18]

3
00:01:45,710 --> 00:01:47,170
What are you doing, Honey?

4
00:01:49,430 --> 00:01:50,430
Beef pancakes?

5
00:01:50,650 --> 00:01:52,580
Yes, I looked up the recipe online.

6
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:54,710
Jiale loves the pancakes
Leilei made the most.

7
00:01:54,710 --> 00:01:55,410
I know.

8
00:01:59,310 --> 00:02:00,020
Honey,

9
00:02:00,430 --> 00:02:01,890
thanks for your hard work.

10
00:02:03,090 --> 00:02:04,090
It's my pleasure.

11
00:02:05,350 --> 00:02:06,680
There's so much smoke.

12
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:08,720
You're awake?

13
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:11,450
What's this smell? It smells great!

14
00:02:11,450 --> 00:02:13,150
Didn't you say you were craving this?

15
00:02:13,150 --> 00:02:14,810
Your favorite beef pancakes.

16
00:02:16,060 --> 00:02:18,860
But it's quite difficult
to make it for the first time.

17
00:02:18,860 --> 00:02:20,720
It looks like the house is on fire.

18
00:02:21,030 --> 00:02:21,560
Honey,

19
00:02:21,650 --> 00:02:22,750
the smoke is too thick.

20
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:23,750
Please help open the windows

21
00:02:23,750 --> 00:02:25,610
-and the door to air it out.
-Okay.

22
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:27,610
The range hood doesn't help at all.

23
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:29,870
Jiale.

24
00:02:30,310 --> 00:02:30,770
Come on,

25
00:02:31,870 --> 00:02:32,730
help me taste it

26
00:02:32,870 --> 00:02:34,670
and see if it's the right flavor.

27
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,079
Not bad.

28
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,010
Not bad, huh?

29
00:02:40,150 --> 00:02:40,840
But

30
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:42,280
the ones Godmother made

31
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:45,079
seemed to have a slightly pungent taste.

32
00:02:46,470 --> 00:02:47,400
A pungent taste?

33
00:02:48,310 --> 00:02:50,110
Could it be Sichuan peppercorn?

34
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:50,620
Yeah.

35
00:02:50,870 --> 00:02:51,910
The taste of Sichuan peppercorn.

36
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:52,960
Then f-forget about this one.

37
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:53,890
I'll improve it.

38
00:02:54,750 --> 00:02:55,550
Just a moment.

39
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:58,050
Look at how serious you are.

40
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,680
You're almost
like a scientific researcher.

41
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:01,940
Of course I'm serious.

42
00:03:02,310 --> 00:03:03,750
Jiale is my buddy now.

43
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:04,800
I must help my buddy

44
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,750
fulfill his wish.

45
00:03:05,750 --> 00:03:06,160
Right?

46
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,170
Thanks, big bro.

47
00:03:07,310 --> 00:03:08,310
Don't mention it.

48
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:10,240
Seems like I can only be an assistant

49
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,640
and dispose of the trash.

50
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:13,510
Honey,

51
00:03:13,750 --> 00:03:15,520
there's some chicken left from last night.

52
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:17,360
Aren't there
quite a few stray cats downstairs?

53
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:19,030
Do you want to take Jiale
to feed them together?

54
00:03:19,030 --> 00:03:20,079
I want to go.

55
00:03:20,079 --> 00:03:21,470
Jiale, give me some time.

56
00:03:21,470 --> 00:03:22,240
I'll wrap it up real quick.

57
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:24,040
It will be ready when you come up.

58
00:03:25,310 --> 00:03:26,770
Jiale, change your shoes.

59
00:03:26,870 --> 00:03:27,560
It's raining outside.

60
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,760
I'll get an umbrella.

61
00:03:35,310 --> 00:03:36,950
Honey, we'll be right back.

62
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:37,590
Okay.

63
00:03:37,590 --> 00:03:38,750
I'll leave the door open.

64
00:03:38,750 --> 00:03:39,240
Okay.

65
00:03:45,630 --> 00:03:47,329
Where are the kitties?

66
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,150
It's pouring rain today.

67
00:03:49,150 --> 00:03:51,480
Are the cats all hiding
and not coming out?

68
00:03:57,870 --> 00:03:59,130
Where are the kitties?

69
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:01,060
Come on.

70
00:04:01,630 --> 00:04:03,160
Help Mom open the trash can.

71
00:04:04,710 --> 00:04:05,310
Thank you.

72
00:04:07,870 --> 00:04:09,310
They seem to be over there.

73
00:04:09,310 --> 00:04:09,750
Look.

74
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:11,280
Let's go take a look.

75
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,680
I even heard a cat meowing.

76
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:14,310
Really?

77
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:19,149
They really are here.

78
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:19,690
Look.

79
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:20,829
What are they eating?

80
00:04:20,829 --> 00:04:22,630
They already have something to eat.

81
00:04:22,630 --> 00:04:23,760
Has anyone fed them?

82
00:04:34,170 --> 00:04:34,680
Mom,

83
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,540
what is that?

84
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:37,000
What is it?

85
00:04:40,390 --> 00:04:41,450
Don't look, Jiale.

86
00:04:41,870 --> 00:04:43,070
I-Is it Cola?

87
00:04:43,070 --> 00:04:44,240
Don't look, don't look.

88
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:44,510
Don't.

89
00:04:44,510 --> 00:04:45,070
Cola!

90
00:04:45,070 --> 00:04:45,730
Don't look.

91
00:04:46,270 --> 00:04:47,310
It's Cola!

92
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,100
I really closed the cage.

93
00:04:57,310 --> 00:04:58,720
I remember it clearly.

94
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:01,010
Did you forget to lock it?

95
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:04,480
You have to twist it to the right
after closing the door.

96
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:06,230
I did twist it. I did.

97
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:08,270
I remember I did this.

98
00:05:10,510 --> 00:05:11,920
But after dinner yesterday,

99
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:12,630
Jiale and I

100
00:05:12,630 --> 00:05:14,040
never fed Cola again.

101
00:05:14,390 --> 00:05:17,390
It couldn't have opened the cage
and run out by itself.

102
00:05:27,870 --> 00:05:28,690
Jiale,

103
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:29,860
stop crying.

104
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:31,860
Mom will go with you

105
00:05:32,270 --> 00:05:33,570
to bury Cola.

106
00:05:34,070 --> 00:05:35,390
We'll get a new one.

107
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,330
Is that good?

108
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,570
No!

109
00:05:37,630 --> 00:05:39,290
It's not the same at all!

110
00:05:39,510 --> 00:05:42,159
Cola is dead and will never come back!

111
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:44,390
It was you who killed Cola.

112
00:05:44,390 --> 00:05:46,110
Why don't you admit it?

113
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,070
It really wasn't me.

114
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,480
You are always like this.

115
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:51,630
You got Grandpa killed back then

116
00:05:51,630 --> 00:05:53,800
and left Grandma alone
for the rest of her life.

117
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:55,409
You're so selfish!

118
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,430
You made mistakes
and didn't dare to admit them.

119
00:05:57,430 --> 00:05:59,290
Instead, you only blamed others.

120
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:00,720
Jiale.

121
00:06:05,310 --> 00:06:06,000
Jiale.

122
00:06:08,510 --> 00:06:09,870
Jiale, open the door

123
00:06:09,870 --> 00:06:11,330
and let Mom explain, okay?

124
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,630
I don't want to hear it!

125
00:06:12,630 --> 00:06:14,560
I only want Cola back!

126
00:06:15,070 --> 00:06:16,800
Open the door first, okay?

127
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,390
Let Mom explain, please.

128
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,240
Jiale.

129
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:22,600
Jia...

130
00:06:24,610 --> 00:06:25,750
Give him some time.

131
00:06:26,310 --> 00:06:28,240
You also heard what he just said.

132
00:06:29,270 --> 00:06:31,130
How could he think of me like that?

133
00:06:31,690 --> 00:06:33,620
He's just overwhelmed with grief.

134
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,310
Facing Cola's death,

135
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,880
finding someone to blame

136
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:38,780
can make him feel a little better.

137
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:41,520
This is a common way people
deal with grief.

138
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:44,070
When Leilei and your mom passed away,

139
00:06:44,070 --> 00:06:45,330
didn't you do the same?

140
00:06:48,070 --> 00:06:48,850
Yesterday,

141
00:06:49,450 --> 00:06:50,710
after feeding Cola,

142
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:54,140
I really did close the cage.

143
00:06:55,510 --> 00:06:56,920
I really twisted it.

144
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,480
I remember it clearly.

145
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:01,600
I admit,

146
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:04,540
when I opened the window and the door,

147
00:07:04,630 --> 00:07:05,800
I didn't notice

148
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,600
if Cola was still in the cage.

149
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:11,460
If only I hadn't opened
the windows and the door.

150
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,330
What do you mean by that?

151
00:07:17,270 --> 00:07:18,680
So you're blaming me now?

152
00:07:19,270 --> 00:07:20,680
It's because I told you to open the door

153
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:21,870
that Cola ran away?

154
00:07:23,950 --> 00:07:25,270
I didn't mean that.

155
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,520
But the way you put it just now

156
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:29,390
will make Jiale think

157
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,190
it's all my fault.

158
00:07:31,830 --> 00:07:33,210
So Jiale was right.

159
00:07:34,070 --> 00:07:36,270
You just need someone to take the blame,

160
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,600
someone to blame.

161
00:07:38,070 --> 00:07:39,720
So that person is me now.

162
00:07:39,890 --> 00:07:41,040
I didn't say that.

163
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:42,720
I just feel...

164
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:43,830
"I," "I," "I."

165
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:46,170
"I feel," "I think," "I remember."

166
00:07:46,270 --> 00:07:48,130
Why do you only think of yourself?

167
00:07:48,159 --> 00:07:49,390
Other people's efforts and feelings

168
00:07:49,390 --> 00:07:50,520
mean nothing to you.

169
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:56,800
Don't twist my words.

170
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,530
Let's talk inside the room.

171
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:13,560
I'll be blunt.

172
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,580
You say you want to comfort Jiale,

173
00:08:17,390 --> 00:08:20,120
but have you ever
really cared about his feelings?

174
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:20,950
He's only 10.

175
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,630
Do you even know how much pressure

176
00:08:23,630 --> 00:08:25,120
and grievance he has endured

177
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,320
because of your mess?

178
00:08:26,510 --> 00:08:27,840
When he chatted with me,

179
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:30,920
he told me that his classmates were
all gossiping about you,

180
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:32,250
which made him so upset,

181
00:08:32,390 --> 00:08:34,190
but he didn't know how to refute.

182
00:08:34,510 --> 00:08:37,110
He has endured
all of this silently by himself.

183
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:39,960
I admit

184
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,440
that my situation

185
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,730
would make Jiale very confused

186
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:45,990
and upset.

187
00:08:46,630 --> 00:08:48,360
Because it's too complicated.

188
00:08:49,030 --> 00:08:51,430
I don't know
how to explain it to him either.

189
00:08:51,630 --> 00:08:53,360
But that's a different matter.

190
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:55,720
I really locked the cage.

191
00:08:55,740 --> 00:08:57,340
You can't accuse me wrongly.

192
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,320
Yeah, yeah.

193
00:09:00,390 --> 00:09:02,120
You are always a victim,

194
00:09:02,630 --> 00:09:04,320
always the one getting hurt.

195
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,280
Your father's death,

196
00:09:06,910 --> 00:09:08,720
your mother's lifelong pain,

197
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,790
your one-night stand with Lu,

198
00:09:10,790 --> 00:09:11,910
and Jiale's birth.

199
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,010
Tell me.

200
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:16,170
Do you really have no responsibility
for all of this?

201
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,000
You don't dare to accept

202
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:19,670
the fact that your life was
messed up by yourself.

203
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:21,390
So you must always be right,

204
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:22,270
righteous,

205
00:09:22,790 --> 00:09:23,720
and fair.

206
00:09:24,380 --> 00:09:26,670
It's always other people
who cause mistakes.

207
00:09:26,670 --> 00:09:27,720
To prove this,

208
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,670
you even tried to put the blame

209
00:09:29,670 --> 00:09:30,670
on me just now

210
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:33,050
in order to ease your own guilt.

211
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:36,630
No.

212
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,130
That's not true.

213
00:09:39,750 --> 00:09:40,160
I...

214
00:09:40,630 --> 00:09:41,200
No.

215
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,200
At this moment,

216
00:09:42,710 --> 00:09:44,240
when Jiale is in deep grief,

217
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:46,790
shouldn't you, his mother,

218
00:09:46,790 --> 00:09:48,610
do whatever it takes

219
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:50,870
to make him feel a bit better?

220
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:52,750
But what you care about is still

221
00:09:52,750 --> 00:09:54,610
whether you are wrongly accused.

222
00:10:21,910 --> 00:10:22,390
Hello?

223
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,040
What's up?

224
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:25,940
Is this Xiao Su?

225
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:28,790
I'm a police officer
from Dongqiao Police Station in Wuzhou.

226
00:10:28,790 --> 00:10:30,990
Your mother, Hua Sanmei, is with us now.

227
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:36,200
Hello.

228
00:10:37,910 --> 00:10:39,240
What happened to my mom?

229
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:42,150
You know the girl
who lives with your mother,

230
00:10:42,150 --> 00:10:42,750
right?

231
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:46,810
She is a patient of mine.

232
00:10:47,500 --> 00:10:48,710
I am a psychiatrist.

233
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,900
This patient has no other relatives,

234
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:55,110
and her stepfather is unwilling
to take care of her.

235
00:10:55,110 --> 00:10:57,560
Besides, her condition
took a turn for the worse a while ago.

236
00:10:57,560 --> 00:10:58,630
The nursing hospital raised its prices,

237
00:10:58,630 --> 00:11:00,000
and she couldn't afford them.

238
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,560
So I took her to my hometown

239
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,740
and let my mom take care of her.

240
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:05,870
But your mother insists

241
00:11:05,870 --> 00:11:07,000
that this girl is

242
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,750
your sister, Xiao Yuan.

243
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:13,590
My sister

244
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:16,400
didn't get along with our family

245
00:11:18,150 --> 00:11:20,210
and ran away from home many years ago.

246
00:11:20,580 --> 00:11:22,780
There has been no news of her ever since.

247
00:11:22,910 --> 00:11:24,440
It was a huge blow to my mom.

248
00:11:25,450 --> 00:11:26,780
Maybe deep down inside,

249
00:11:27,670 --> 00:11:29,870
she really hopes that girl is my sister.

250
00:11:30,390 --> 00:11:31,770
I think this is good, too.

251
00:11:31,770 --> 00:11:34,300
If she takes care of her
like her own daughter,

252
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:36,570
it's also good for the patient.

253
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:39,670
Did you prescribe the medicine
for this girl?

254
00:11:40,680 --> 00:11:41,880
Yes, I prescribed it.

255
00:11:43,910 --> 00:11:45,570
Which hospital do you work at?

256
00:11:45,710 --> 00:11:48,390
I work in the Psychiatry Department
at Lihai Renxin Hospital

257
00:11:48,390 --> 00:11:49,050
as a doctor.

258
00:11:50,270 --> 00:11:50,800
Officer,

259
00:11:51,680 --> 00:11:53,280
I want to explain something.

260
00:11:53,910 --> 00:11:56,340
When I retook the college entrance exam,
for my student status,

261
00:11:56,340 --> 00:11:58,000
I changed my name to Luo Liang.

262
00:11:58,620 --> 00:11:59,920
My dad got this done.

263
00:12:00,390 --> 00:12:01,990
My mom doesn't know about it.

264
00:12:04,870 --> 00:12:05,440
Officer,

265
00:12:06,930 --> 00:12:08,280
what on earth happened?

266
00:12:09,380 --> 00:12:11,580
Your mother gave her
3 times the dosage.

267
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:13,640
That was a lethal dose.

268
00:12:16,910 --> 00:12:17,790
My mom is undereducated

269
00:12:17,790 --> 00:12:19,270
and can't read the medicine names.

270
00:12:19,270 --> 00:12:22,000
I taught her how to give them
based on colors and sizes.

271
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:24,120
Which medicine did she wrongly give Shan?

272
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,650
How is Shan doing right now?

273
00:12:26,550 --> 00:12:29,240
Luckily, your mother
called an ambulance in time.

274
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:30,840
So the girl barely survived.

275
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:38,080
That's great.

276
00:12:39,530 --> 00:12:40,730
Thank God she's fine.

277
00:12:50,320 --> 00:12:51,080
How did your mother

278
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:52,320
get this medicine?

279
00:12:53,910 --> 00:12:54,910
Here's the thing.

280
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:01,060
It's prescription drugs,

281
00:13:01,630 --> 00:13:03,090
which can't be couriered.

282
00:13:03,490 --> 00:13:05,150
So I sent them by regular mail.

283
00:13:06,030 --> 00:13:07,880
What's this girl's real name?

284
00:13:08,320 --> 00:13:10,580
Which sanatorium did you take her out of?

285
00:13:11,670 --> 00:13:13,000
Her name is Qiao Zishan.

286
00:13:15,280 --> 00:13:16,740
She's from Harbor Island.

287
00:13:18,450 --> 00:13:21,580
She used to live
in Minkang Sanatorium on Harbor Island.

288
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:25,970
Dr. Luo is

289
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,060
a volunteer doctor

290
00:13:27,150 --> 00:13:28,810
at our sanatorium,

291
00:13:29,170 --> 00:13:31,570
who has taken care
of Zishan for many years.

292
00:13:31,570 --> 00:13:33,480
Zishan's mother died in the fire
set by herself,

293
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:35,360
and it was Dr. Luo
who rushed into the fire

294
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:36,360
and saved Zishan.

295
00:13:36,630 --> 00:13:39,230
She originally planned to study
art and design

296
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:41,630
after graduating from City University.

297
00:13:41,630 --> 00:13:43,740
But her mother suddenly went crazy

298
00:13:43,820 --> 00:13:44,750
and set the fire,

299
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:46,050
destroying her.

300
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:46,870
What a pity.

301
00:13:48,910 --> 00:13:52,120
Were it not for Dr. Luo,
who's been covering her medical bills,

302
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:53,630
she probably would have died long ago,

303
00:13:53,630 --> 00:13:55,160
relying on his stepfather.

304
00:13:55,510 --> 00:13:56,240
Then why did Dr. Luo

305
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:58,030
take Qiao Zishan out of the sanatorium?

306
00:13:58,030 --> 00:13:59,700
Our place was acquired recently,

307
00:13:59,700 --> 00:14:00,840
and all prices went up.

308
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:01,750
No way her stepfather

309
00:14:00,990 --> 00:14:02,880
[Automatic doors. Do not loiter.]

310
00:14:01,750 --> 00:14:02,850
could afford them.

311
00:14:02,940 --> 00:14:04,650
Besides, having an old man

312
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:06,110
take care of a girl

313
00:14:06,390 --> 00:14:08,320
who is not related to him by blood is

314
00:14:08,630 --> 00:14:09,960
not appropriate at all!

315
00:14:10,670 --> 00:14:11,670
I'm a doctor.

316
00:14:14,090 --> 00:14:15,900
I treat every patient equally.

317
00:14:16,410 --> 00:14:19,270
How could he have
any ulterior motives towards her?

318
00:14:19,670 --> 00:14:20,670
Dr. Luo

319
00:14:20,670 --> 00:14:22,330
treats patients all the same.

320
00:14:22,390 --> 00:14:24,630
I think he just has
a benevolent heart as a doctor.

321
00:14:24,630 --> 00:14:27,210
He's especially supportive of the weak

322
00:14:27,270 --> 00:14:28,480
and vulnerable.

323
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:30,000
So, the staff in our place,

324
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:31,000
including me,

325
00:14:31,070 --> 00:14:32,530
all respect him very much.

326
00:14:33,090 --> 00:14:34,750
If there's anything special,

327
00:14:36,670 --> 00:14:37,510
it might be because

328
00:14:37,510 --> 00:14:39,270
I saved her life in the fire.

329
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:44,160
I want her to live well more than anyone.

330
00:14:50,750 --> 00:14:51,550
Wait a moment.

331
00:15:00,930 --> 00:15:01,480
[The First Affiliated Hospital
of Wuzhou Medical University]

332
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:02,180
[Physical Checkup Form]

333
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,640
[Surgery] [Internal Medicine]
[Blood Routine]

334
00:15:07,730 --> 00:15:08,370
Xiao Su.

335
00:15:09,750 --> 00:15:11,100
We just verified it.

336
00:15:11,670 --> 00:15:13,540
What you said is basically true.

337
00:15:13,870 --> 00:15:14,980
From what we know,

338
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:16,750
your mother has also been taking

339
00:15:16,750 --> 00:15:18,150
good care of Qiao Zishan.

340
00:15:18,360 --> 00:15:20,760
This incident might indeed be a slip-up,

341
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:23,680
and we'll close the case as an accident.

342
00:15:23,790 --> 00:15:26,130
But you must remind your mother

343
00:15:26,360 --> 00:15:28,560
of never making the same mistake again.

344
00:15:30,170 --> 00:15:31,220
That's for sure.

345
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:33,670
I will.

346
00:15:51,830 --> 00:15:52,810
[Calls]

347
00:15:53,110 --> 00:15:57,520
[July 15, 2019, Monday]

348
00:16:11,370 --> 00:16:13,490
[July 15, 2019, Monday]

349
00:16:35,890 --> 00:16:39,010
[July 15, 2019, Monday]

350
00:16:48,630 --> 00:16:49,430
Jiale.

351
00:16:49,840 --> 00:16:50,960
Where are you going?

352
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:51,960
To my dad's place.

353
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:54,460
I've already talked to him
and Ms. Fang Fang.

354
00:16:54,870 --> 00:16:55,910
Let Mom give you a lift then.

355
00:16:55,910 --> 00:16:56,440
No need!

356
00:16:56,440 --> 00:16:57,910
I don't need you to give me a lift.

357
00:16:57,910 --> 00:16:59,370
I'll have my dad pick me up.

358
00:16:59,510 --> 00:17:00,120
Jiale.

359
00:17:00,870 --> 00:17:02,070
I'll go down with you.

360
00:17:02,320 --> 00:17:03,580
It's raining outside.

361
00:17:33,110 --> 00:17:33,640
Hello.

362
00:17:33,640 --> 00:17:34,310
Hello, hello.

363
00:17:34,310 --> 00:17:35,200
Here's his luggage.

364
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:35,530
Okay.

365
00:17:36,030 --> 00:17:37,390
Please take care of him
for a couple of days.

366
00:17:37,390 --> 00:17:38,440
Of course. As I should.

367
00:17:38,440 --> 00:17:39,570
All right, let's go.

368
00:17:40,110 --> 00:17:40,510
Jiale.

369
00:17:45,070 --> 00:17:46,100
Don't be sad.

370
00:17:46,480 --> 00:17:47,730
Stop crying.

371
00:17:52,390 --> 00:17:53,920
When Jiale is in deep grief,

372
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:57,120
shouldn't you, his mother,

373
00:17:57,590 --> 00:17:59,530
do whatever it takes

374
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:01,400
to make him feel a bit better?

375
00:18:33,070 --> 00:18:33,910
Thank you

376
00:18:33,960 --> 00:18:35,620
for dropping Jiale off for me.

377
00:18:38,440 --> 00:18:39,570
I am his father, too.

378
00:18:41,240 --> 00:18:41,920
I'm sorry.

379
00:18:45,030 --> 00:18:45,920
You are right.

380
00:18:48,480 --> 00:18:50,480
I really am not a good mother.

381
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:07,820
No matter what mistakes you make,

382
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:10,970
we will always forgive you.

383
00:19:12,240 --> 00:19:13,480
We are family.

384
00:19:20,290 --> 00:19:21,070
It's fine.

385
00:19:23,070 --> 00:19:23,980
Let him stay there for a few days.

386
00:19:23,980 --> 00:19:24,780
It'll be okay.

387
00:19:28,920 --> 00:19:29,520
Don't cry.

388
00:19:52,310 --> 00:19:53,570
Let me take a break, take a break.

389
00:19:53,570 --> 00:19:54,020
I can't

390
00:19:54,110 --> 00:19:55,510
do this anymore, Paw Patrol.

391
00:19:55,510 --> 00:19:57,570
I surrender. I'm out. I can't do this.

392
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:02,940
Tell me about the case.

393
00:20:08,750 --> 00:20:09,640
He Xiao's son

394
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:11,640
personally confirmed

395
00:20:11,640 --> 00:20:13,680
that his private tutor
at that time was called Luo Liang.

396
00:20:13,680 --> 00:20:14,280
Moreover,

397
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:16,680
He Xiao also financially supported

398
00:20:16,830 --> 00:20:18,830
Luo Liang's studies on Harbor Island.

399
00:20:18,830 --> 00:20:21,560
That can only prove
that they were lovers at most.

400
00:20:21,770 --> 00:20:23,410
It doesn't mean he is Mister.

401
00:20:24,230 --> 00:20:25,790
Nor does it prove
that he has anything to do

402
00:20:25,790 --> 00:20:26,990
with He Xiao's death.

403
00:20:27,550 --> 00:20:28,160
I know.

404
00:20:29,350 --> 00:20:30,950
So I went straight to see him.

405
00:20:31,710 --> 00:20:33,770
I even booked an expert appointment.

406
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:35,000
Sit down, please.

407
00:20:36,160 --> 00:20:37,090
Just put it here.

408
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:40,800
Is there anything wrong?

409
00:20:40,960 --> 00:20:42,360
He's completely normal.

410
00:20:42,920 --> 00:20:44,790
I can't see any flaws at all.

411
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:47,520
So I don't know what to do now.

412
00:20:48,030 --> 00:20:50,070
Do you think I should talk to Ms. Yan

413
00:20:52,070 --> 00:20:53,450
and tell her

414
00:20:53,630 --> 00:20:54,600
all we know?

415
00:20:58,480 --> 00:21:00,010
What are you worried about?

416
00:21:01,510 --> 00:21:03,120
They just got married.

417
00:21:03,830 --> 00:21:05,210
From what Ms. Yan said,

418
00:21:05,650 --> 00:21:07,450
they're pretty happy together.

419
00:21:08,480 --> 00:21:09,680
We are just guessing now.

420
00:21:09,680 --> 00:21:11,030
What if he is not Mister?

421
00:21:11,330 --> 00:21:12,680
If I go to Ms. Yan

422
00:21:12,680 --> 00:21:13,240
and say,

423
00:21:14,400 --> 00:21:15,270
"Your husband is

424
00:21:15,270 --> 00:21:17,280
the boss of Xia Yi and the others.

425
00:21:17,480 --> 00:21:18,750
About that PUA stuff,

426
00:21:18,750 --> 00:21:20,440
they've learned it all from your husband."

427
00:21:20,440 --> 00:21:21,970
Ms. Yan would lose her mind!

428
00:21:23,960 --> 00:21:25,380
Chief Hu said before

429
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:28,040
that when we solve cases,

430
00:21:28,480 --> 00:21:30,080
we must presume innocence.

431
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:32,420
While pursuing the truth,

432
00:21:32,960 --> 00:21:35,310
we must also seek kindness and compassion.

433
00:21:35,310 --> 00:21:35,880
Right?

434
00:21:56,350 --> 00:21:59,720
[Luo Liang] [Xiao Su] [Wuzhou]

435
00:21:57,110 --> 00:21:57,960
You made this?

436
00:21:59,630 --> 00:22:02,440
No kidding. I didn't stay
in the Special Crimes Unit for nothing.

437
00:22:02,440 --> 00:22:03,120
Look.

438
00:22:04,350 --> 00:22:05,000
Luo Liang.

439
00:22:05,680 --> 00:22:06,370
No.

440
00:22:06,790 --> 00:22:08,350
He wasn't called Luo Liang back then.

441
00:22:08,350 --> 00:22:09,030
Xiao Su

442
00:22:08,600 --> 00:22:13,040
[Dongguang, First Love, Xu Jingyun]

443
00:22:10,040 --> 00:22:12,270
got admitted to Nanshan Medical University

444
00:22:12,270 --> 00:22:13,470
in Dongguang in 1999.

445
00:22:15,770 --> 00:22:16,490
In 2000,

446
00:22:17,070 --> 00:22:20,200
he was sentenced to 3 years in prison
for attempted rape.

447
00:22:20,350 --> 00:22:22,030
One year after his release from prison,

448
00:22:22,030 --> 00:22:23,110
in 2004,

449
00:22:24,480 --> 00:22:26,240
he changed his face and identity

450
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:27,280
and got admitted

451
00:22:27,310 --> 00:22:30,070
to Tianfu Medical University
in Chengyu City again.

452
00:22:27,410 --> 00:22:28,990
[Chengyu, Private Tutor, He Xiao]

453
00:22:30,070 --> 00:22:31,150
He Xiao's home was

454
00:22:31,590 --> 00:22:32,920
in Chengyu at that time.

455
00:22:33,680 --> 00:22:34,980
In 2007,

456
00:22:35,350 --> 00:22:38,410
Luo Liang was hired
as a private tutor in He Xiao's home.

457
00:22:39,350 --> 00:22:42,270
My mom often invited him
to stay for dinner.

458
00:22:43,410 --> 00:22:45,730
We were like a family.

459
00:22:48,590 --> 00:22:49,920
In 2009,

460
00:22:50,070 --> 00:22:50,920
Xie Ke

461
00:22:51,890 --> 00:22:52,680
went to Chengyu

462
00:22:52,090 --> 00:22:56,010
[Bingyuan, Volunteer, Xie Ke]

463
00:22:52,680 --> 00:22:53,830
to participate

464
00:22:53,850 --> 00:22:57,000
in the skating competition
of the Oya Youth Games that year.

465
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:57,930
I've checked it.

466
00:22:58,270 --> 00:22:59,530
In the Games that year,

467
00:22:59,830 --> 00:23:01,680
countless students
from Tianfu Medical University

468
00:23:01,680 --> 00:23:03,610
served as volunteers in the arena.

469
00:23:05,690 --> 00:23:07,290
Sir, please have some water.

470
00:23:13,680 --> 00:23:14,480
Here is water.

471
00:23:29,030 --> 00:23:32,880
[Oya Youth Games
Figure Skating Championships]

472
00:23:32,940 --> 00:23:34,270
[For Media]

473
00:23:41,990 --> 00:23:43,290
For Xie Ke,

474
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:46,110
he ruthlessly dumped He Xiao,

475
00:23:46,110 --> 00:23:47,910
even though He Xiao was pregnant

476
00:23:48,200 --> 00:23:49,510
with Luo Liang's child at that time.

477
00:23:49,510 --> 00:23:50,160
Exactly.

478
00:23:50,550 --> 00:23:51,750
Early in 2010,

479
00:23:51,880 --> 00:23:53,310
He Xiao was unwilling to let go.

480
00:23:53,310 --> 00:23:54,510
To win back her lover,

481
00:23:54,570 --> 00:23:57,470
she went to Bingyuan City to find Xie Ke

482
00:23:57,680 --> 00:23:59,940
and begged her to break up with Luo Liang.

483
00:24:00,200 --> 00:24:01,330
I'd give up my family

484
00:24:01,790 --> 00:24:03,340
as well as my child.

485
00:24:03,510 --> 00:24:04,970
All I want is him.

486
00:24:05,270 --> 00:24:06,830
But the begging didn't work.

487
00:24:06,830 --> 00:24:08,880
He Xiao committed suicide in Bingyuan,

488
00:24:08,880 --> 00:24:11,610
showing Xie Ke her despair through death,

489
00:24:11,960 --> 00:24:13,640
and demonstrating her love for Luo Liang.

490
00:24:13,640 --> 00:24:14,310
Exactly.

491
00:24:14,930 --> 00:24:17,150
Not long after He Xiao's suicide,

492
00:24:17,170 --> 00:24:18,430
before a competition,

493
00:24:18,750 --> 00:24:20,960
Xie Ke suddenly learned about this

494
00:24:20,960 --> 00:24:22,160
from a companion of hers.

495
00:24:22,160 --> 00:24:22,750
But I do know

496
00:24:22,750 --> 00:24:24,640
even the greatest love
can't be built on someone's death,

497
00:24:24,640 --> 00:24:26,030
for there will be retribution!

498
00:24:26,030 --> 00:24:27,490
She was all over the place.

499
00:24:27,750 --> 00:24:29,070
That was why she made a mistake

500
00:24:29,070 --> 00:24:30,680
when performing that difficult move.

501
00:24:30,680 --> 00:24:31,550
Then her partner

502
00:24:31,550 --> 00:24:34,420
touched the wound from her recent tattoo,

503
00:24:35,790 --> 00:24:37,270
causing Xie Ke to accidentally fall

504
00:24:37,270 --> 00:24:38,550
in that competition.

505
00:24:44,750 --> 00:24:46,200
In 2010,

506
00:24:46,450 --> 00:24:48,790
Luo Liang had already used
the money given by He Xiao

507
00:24:48,790 --> 00:24:51,350
to get into the Medical School
of Xiangjiang University on Harbor Island

508
00:24:51,350 --> 00:24:52,160
for his PhD.

509
00:24:54,830 --> 00:24:56,090
Just a few years later,

510
00:24:56,460 --> 00:24:57,950
[Shenchuan, Wei Zhihua]

511
00:24:56,550 --> 00:24:57,830
Wei Zhihua, a hairdresser

512
00:24:57,830 --> 00:25:00,230
working in Shenchuan, committed suicide.

513
00:25:00,510 --> 00:25:01,240
Yes,

514
00:25:00,530 --> 00:25:03,220
[Chloe]

515
00:25:01,240 --> 00:25:02,470
Zhihua.

516
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:04,610
She was so pretty.

517
00:25:05,030 --> 00:25:06,090
Don't you get it?

518
00:25:06,640 --> 00:25:07,440
I guess

519
00:25:07,440 --> 00:25:10,900
it's highly likely
that during Luo Liang's doctoral studies,

520
00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:13,970
while traveling
between Harbor Island and Shenchuan,

521
00:25:13,970 --> 00:25:15,410
he met this hairdresser.

522
00:25:22,510 --> 00:25:25,240
Because he made an acquaintance
with the hairdresser, Wei Zhihua,

523
00:25:25,240 --> 00:25:27,890
Luo Liang dumped Xie Ke.

524
00:25:34,160 --> 00:25:35,890
Where have you been for so long?

525
00:25:41,590 --> 00:25:43,650
I've been studying on Harbor Island.

526
00:25:44,410 --> 00:25:46,540
Then why didn't you come back to see me?

527
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:49,720
As you know,

528
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:52,100
I'm very busy with my coursework.

529
00:25:55,270 --> 00:25:57,830
Did you fall in love
with someone else again?

530
00:25:59,850 --> 00:26:01,310
What kind of person is she?

531
00:26:09,590 --> 00:26:11,030
She is a very simple girl,

532
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:14,590
unlike you,

533
00:26:15,330 --> 00:26:17,390
who are so aloof and hard to approach.

534
00:26:17,860 --> 00:26:19,430
I am not like that.

535
00:26:21,400 --> 00:26:22,460
She loves me so much

536
00:26:23,290 --> 00:26:24,960
that when I said I wanted a child,

537
00:26:24,960 --> 00:26:25,880
she agreed immediately.

538
00:26:25,880 --> 00:26:27,200
I love you, too.

539
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:28,510
I can do the same.

540
00:26:31,210 --> 00:26:32,610
I don't want to lie to you.

541
00:26:34,070 --> 00:26:35,870
So don't lie to yourself either.

542
00:26:38,390 --> 00:26:39,390
Look at yourself.

543
00:26:43,410 --> 00:26:44,870
Look at the way you are now.

544
00:26:48,660 --> 00:26:50,460
How are we supposed to continue?

545
00:26:51,930 --> 00:26:52,880
No.

546
00:26:52,880 --> 00:26:54,480
Please don't leave me.

547
00:26:54,510 --> 00:26:55,770
-Let me go.
-I'm now...

548
00:26:56,310 --> 00:26:57,170
Don't go.

549
00:26:57,720 --> 00:26:58,480
No.

550
00:27:00,440 --> 00:27:01,520
L-Look.

551
00:27:01,550 --> 00:27:02,640
Look, I can.

552
00:27:02,640 --> 00:27:04,030
I'm recovering now.

553
00:27:04,200 --> 00:27:05,110
I'm begging you.

554
00:27:05,110 --> 00:27:06,880
Please give me another chance, okay?

555
00:27:06,880 --> 00:27:08,710
Don't leave me.

556
00:27:08,880 --> 00:27:10,350
Come on. Look at yourself.

557
00:27:10,710 --> 00:27:12,510
Look at the way you are right now.

558
00:27:17,310 --> 00:27:18,970
Do you still look like a woman?

559
00:28:15,030 --> 00:28:16,590
In the autumn of 2011,

560
00:28:17,070 --> 00:28:20,310
Xie Ke traveled all the way
from Bingyuan to Chengyu,

561
00:28:20,310 --> 00:28:22,270
and at the stadium
where she once competed in the Games,

562
00:28:22,270 --> 00:28:23,590
she leaped to her death.

563
00:28:23,590 --> 00:28:24,480
People all thought

564
00:28:24,480 --> 00:28:27,590
she was commemorating the place
where she once won the championship.

